entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have contacted Kaesii about an aquisition mission. The plans to a prototype military speeder are up for grabs.
entries.journal_entry_description: One of the most important aspects of being a spy is gaining contacts. People that will help you out and offer you missions. Lercer has sent you a comm about a possible contact. It would be a good idea to see what this contact has in mind for you.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: I've got a contact for you. Meet her at the Lucky Despot in Mos Eisley, her name is Kaesii you can't miss her. She says she has a mission for you. Good luck!
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Lercer contacted you about a contact at the Lucky Despot in Mos Eisley. He says this is a mission for you.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You need to meet your contact in the Lucky Despot cantina in Mos Eisley. It's in the big wrecked spaceship.
